rows.label: qst201005_0050
rows.name: But still, you've fallen into our trap.

rows.label: qst201005_0070
rows.name: Pincer attack?! We in tight squeeze!

rows.label: qst201005_0080
rows.name: Looks like they read us like a book.

rows.label: qst201005_0090
rows.name: Heh heh heh... You thought you had us, did you?

rows.label: qst201005_0100
rows.name: I've put paid to a thousand fools like you in my time.

rows.label: qst201005_0110
rows.name: And you thought I wouldn't see right through your little plan?

rows.label: qst201005_0120
rows.name:
I think your little soldier friends
have already copped it about now.

rows.label: qst201005_0130
rows.name: I think you underestimate the Superbian Empire.

rows.label: qst201005_0140
rows.name:
Heh heh. I'm not so sure. We're quite the
capable bunch too, you know.

rows.label: qst201005_0150
rows.name:
Since we're putting all the Core Crystals
we've taken to veeeery good use...

rows.label: qst201005_0160
rows.name:
Well, we'll just have to put those skills
to the test then, won't we?

rows.label: qst201005_0170
rows.name: Heh heh... I'm gonna enjoy this.
